{"TopicId":156332,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Weird sight phenomenon","CreatedByName":"rustysocket","CreatedById":152230,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-12T07:39:33Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"rustysocket","CreatedById":152230,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-12T07:39:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI tried googling this with no luck so i thought I should ask it here. Something i\u0027ve noticed is that if you flash the lights on and off quickly, keeping your head completely still, you see a very detailed black and white image of what you were looking at when you flashed the light. It lasts about 5 seconds and disappears if you move your head. I decided to experiment with it and i found it\u0027ll disappear if you put your hand in what would be your field of view and if you close your eyes right after you flash the lights you still see the image (pretty trippy). Do any of you know what\u0027s going on or is this new information?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-02-12T07:40:31Z\u0022 title=\u002202/12/2017 07:40  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 12, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by rustysocket\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GDJ","CreatedById":58462,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-12T08:04:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, certain illicit drugs have been known to do this....apart from that, it\u0027s probably just neurochemical residue from your retinas.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nEither that, or get off the caffeine late at night. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Raging Sandwich","CreatedById":164377,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-12T13:21:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI may have to try this. Hope I don\u0027t have epilepsy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pxi","CreatedById":78711,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-12T13:35:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWouldn\u0027t be related to the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dreamachine\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EDream Machine\u003C/a\u003E popularized by Brion Gyson, would it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-12T16:53:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEither this is an \u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_optical_illusions\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Eafterimage illusion\u003C/a\u003E, or you have a trouble: \u003Cem\u003Ethey\u003C/em\u003E are here and know where you are...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-02-12T16:53:11Z\u0022 title=\u002202/12/2017 04:53  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 12, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"rustysocket","CreatedById":152230,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-12T20:10:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think you got it. They need to make a kerbal thumbs up\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222952828\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022156332\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221486918380\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEither this is an \u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.