\u0022munlander1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, munlander1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf he was, I don\u0027t think he would tell us.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah I don\u0027t think he was. Nor would he tell us.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"munlander1","CreatedById":168560,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-13T00:32:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI tryed this too looking at my desk with an over head thingy to put stuff in and I did see a rough, white outline of it. It was not defined enough to to tell what it was if I did not know what it was.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bill Phil","CreatedById":127797,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-13T01:50:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222953036\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022156332\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221486930215\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152230\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022rustysocket\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, rustysocket said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think you got it. They need to make a kerbal thumbs up\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s the like button on the lower right of the post\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"rustysocket","CreatedById":152230,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-13T02:44:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy don\u0027t you try it before claiming im high\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pxi","CreatedById":78711,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-13T03:07:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222953320\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022156332\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221486945278\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022163034\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheKosanianMethod\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, TheKosanianMethod said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis kinda sounds like you were using illegal substances...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDespite that being the most direct route to altered states of consciousness, other techniques such as meditation, dancing, prayer etc can also induce these sorts of effects.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt might surprise you to know that the chemical released by your pineal gland whilst dreaming (and also at the point of death) is an astoundingly strong psychedelic, which is also found in a wide range of plants which are in fact legal.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYour brain can do weird things when prodded in the right way.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-02-13T03:07:33Z\u0022 title=\u002202/13/2017 03:07  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 13, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by pxi\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"p1t1o","CreatedById":74091,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-13T09:10:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prisoner\u0027s_cinema\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prisoner\u0027s_cinema\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-14T20:36:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think its just a bit of damage in your retina or something that heals quickly. I have the same thing, but its a reddish color with a inner blob of vomit yellow, instead of plain black and white.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}